{
  "texts": [
    "Combining both advantages, we introduce LEAP, a user-friendly interface designed to empower educators to create content and formulate prompts for the LLM.",
    "This enables the provision of specific types of formative feedback and enhances SRL.",
    "In this way, LEAP eliminates the need for programming skills, enabling educators to guide the feedback provided to students more effectively.",
    "In this work, we systematically designed the prompts for the LLMs by splitting them up into three segments (Fig. 1) based on theoretical considerations and prior work.",
    "Here, a prompt is defined as a sequence of instructions given to the LLM to shape the output (here: the formative feedback) provided by the LLM to the students."
  ]
}